                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d04">
                      Decorative designs:
                      <locus target="#37r #45v #52r #82v #151r" facs="037 046 052 083 151"/> (ḥaräg in red ink);
                      <locus target="#62r #74r #88v #113v" facs="062 074 089 114"/> (ḥaräg in red and black ink);
                      <locus target="#116v #123r #150r" facs="117 123 150"/> (alternating red and black dots);
